Huh, the `api_compatibility_test` is failing, and that's probably related to this:

    >>> tf.keras.datasets.boston_housing.print_function
    _Feature((2, 6, 0, 'alpha', 2), (3, 0, 0, 'alpha', 0), 65536)

That file has some very strange lines.  Why would one need to `del print_function`? 

https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/python/keras/datasets/boston_housing/__init__.py#L25
